<h2>-통합 관제 대시보드</h2>
<pre>
Create a highly professional, modern Enterprise Resource & Operations Dashboard for "(주)비에이텍" (Viatech Co., Ltd.), a specialized water pump manufacturing, installation, and repair company. 

The dashboard must be a single-page responsive web application (HTML/CSS with embedded JavaScript for interactive elements) optimized for desktop and tablet screens, featuring an industrial yet clean aesthetic.

### BRAND IDENTITY & COLORS
- Primary: Navy Blue (#1A3A5C) - Represents water technology, engineering expertise, and institutional trust.
- Secondary: Steel Blue & Mint Green (#2E6B9E, #2ECC71) - Used for progress bars and active statuses.
- Accent: Crimson Red (#E74C3C) - Used for urgent alerts, critical inventory depletion, and safety warnings.
- Background: Very light grayish-blue (#F5F7FA) with clean white (#FFFFFF) card containers.

### LAYOUT STRUCTURE (3-Column Grid)
The design must feature a structured 3-column layout:

1. Left Sidebar (Navigation & Profile)
- Top: Viatech Company Logo and Employee Profile Card (name, department, quick logout).
- Middle: Vertical Navigation Menu with smooth hover transitions (Dashboard, Material Inventory, Vehicle Booking, Safety Manuals).
- Bottom: Quick access links for "AI Tech Document Search (NotebookLM Quick link)" and "Administrative Forms Download" with download icons.

2. Center Main Area (Operational Dashboard)
- Top: Three KPI (Key Performance Indicator) Cards:
  a. Today's Dispatches (오늘의 출동 건수) - showing a bright green counter badge.
  b. Pending Inquiries (대기 중인 고객 문의) - showing a yellow counter badge.
  c. Urgent Notice Banner (긴급 공지) - with an animated pulsing red dot.
- Middle Left (Timeline): "Real-time Dispatch & A/S Schedule" showing vertical timeline cards with step badges (Received -> Assigned -> In Progress -> Completed) using distinct color tags.
- Middle Right (Inventory Widget): "Real-time Material & Pump Parts Stock" showing key inventory (Motors, Valves, Pipes) with dynamic Progress Bars. When a stock level is below 20%, the bar turns Crimson Red with a blinking "Low Stock" alert tag.

3. Right Sidebar (Utility & Support)
- Top: "Company Vehicle & Equipment Booking" showing a interactive calendar/time-grid of available vehicles (Unit 1, Unit 2) with booked/available time blocks.
- Middle: "Today's Safety Rules & Equipment Checklist" - Visual, easy-to-read cards reminding workers of mandatory safety gear (Helmets, Safety Boots, Gloves) with illustrative checkmarks.
- Bottom: "Recent Notices & Directory Search" with a fast live search input for internal employee contacts.

### INTERACTIVE FEATURES (Pure JS)
- Toggle tabs or expand categories without reloading the page.
- Make the booking grid responsive on hover.
- Make checkboxes in the Safety Checklist interactive (strikethrough when checked).
- Clean, premium CSS styling with NanumGothic or system sans-serif fonts, using shadow-sm and rounded-lg classes for a modern dashboard look. NO external framework libraries except for FontAwesome icons.

dashboard.html에 전 화면으로 돌아갈 수 잇는 버튼도 추가해줘
</pre>

